# Exclude unnecessary files from Docker build context
# Reduces image size and build time

# .NET build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/

# Test projects
**/*.Tests/

# Development files
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.user
**/*.suo

# Documentation
**/*.md
**/docs/

# Git
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# CI/CD
**/.github/

# Local development
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Node modules (if any)
**/node_modules/

# NuGet packages
**/*.nupkg

# Database files
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
